caption: Table 1: Time per iteration (exponential moving average) for various algorithms in seconds per iteration, for the QUADRATIC OU (EASY) experiments (Figure 2).
description: This table presents the average time taken per iteration for different stochastic optimal control algorithms, namely SOCM, SOCM with constant matrices Mt = I, SOCM-Adjoint, Adjoint, Cross-entropy, Log-variance, Moment, and Variance. The results are based on the QUADRATIC OU (EASY) experiments, as shown in Figure 2 of the paper, and are obtained using an exponential moving average with a coefficient of 0.01 to smooth out the data. The algorithms are implemented using a 16GB V100 GPU.
